    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte et individue Trinitatis. <persName ref="#people/55"
                            key="#Queen">Angilberga</persName>, domni <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/110">Hludovvici</persName> dive memorie piissimi <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperatoris</rs> olim coniux et <rs key="#Queen"
                            >imperatrix</rs> augusta, presens presentibus dixit: Quanto amplius
                        divinis nos obsequiis humiliter subicimus et largitori ac retributori
                        bonorum de his que nobis misericorditer contulit, devote mentis donaria
                        preparamus, tanto amplius supernum circa nos favorem conciliandi credimus et
                        sic a repromissa perhennis vite premia concito cursu pertingere nos posse
                        ipso auxiliante confidimus. Et ideo ego qui supra Angilberga manifeste
                        profiteor eo quod idem excellentissimus imperator dominus et vir meus <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Mention #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >per suum imperialem preceptum</rs> concedere dignatus mihi liberam
                        facultatem ordinandi, distribuendi et potestative faciendi de omnibus rebus
                        meis qualitercumque et in quemcunque michi placuisset; quod etiam gloriosus
                        rex equivocus et avuncolus similiter consentiendo confirmasse dinoscitur,
                        quodque simili modo apostolice sedis pontifices et universales <rs
                            key="#Popes">pape</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/1600" key="#Privileges">Adrianus</persName> et
                            <persName ref="#people/350" key="#Privileges">Johannes</persName>
                        <rs key="#Privileges">suis privilegiis</rs> roborarunt et contradicentes aut
                        inrumpere volentes perpetuo anathemate ligaverunt. Unde nunc ut credo
                        inspirante Deo, imperiali et apostolica autoritate subfulta, deliberavi una
                        cum consensu propincorum et parentum meorum hedifcare <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiam</rs> infra murum <placeName ref="#places/43"
                            key="#Curtes #Churches #Monasteries #Hospitals">urbis
                            Placentine</placeName> ad nomen et gloriam dominice resurrectionis et
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/53"
                            key="#Churches #Monasteries #Hospitals">beatorum apostolorum ac martirum
                            Bartholomei, Sisti et Fabiani</orgName> honorem, ubi volo ut sit
                        instituente et gubernante Domino Christo <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterium</rs> sacrarum puellarum simul etiamo <rs key="#Hospitals"
                            >senodochium</rs> ven. adventantium peregrinorum pro remedio et mercede
                        anime eiusdem clementissimi imperatoris domini et senioris mei et mea seu
                        utriusque prolis nostre nec non etiam nostrorum in commune parentum. Statuo
                        igitur ut habeat supra nominatum cenobium presenti die et hora <rs
                            key="#Curtes">cortes</rs>
                        <rs key="#Demesnes">meas domocoltiles</rs> in <geogName ref="#estates/1500"
                            key="#Curtes #Demesnes">finibus Placentinis</geogName> una cum <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">universis casis et rebus meis</rs> infra vel
                        extra urbem Placentinam quantumcumque michi nunc inibi legibus pertinet aut
                        in antea Deo propicio adquirere potuero. Id sunt in primis corte mea infra
                        ipsam civitatem et aream in qua ipsum cenobium fundatum est, sed et cortes
                        meas in <geogName ref="#estates/319"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve"
                            >Flabiano</geogName>, in <placeName ref="#places/1903"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve"
                                ><geogName ref="#estates/1501" key="#Curtes"
                            >Duliaria</geogName></placeName>, in Fabrica et alias omnes casas et res
                        meas tam de domocoltiles quam <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >massaricias</rs> in eodem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Demesnes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie" ref="#estates/105"
                            >comitatu Placentino</geogName>, una cum <rs key="#Cells/hermitages"
                            >cella</rs> que vocatur <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1508"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >Monasteriolo</orgName>, constructa in loco et fundo <placeName
                            ref="#places/14" key="#Landed_possessions #Cells/hermitages">Caput
                            Trebie</placeName>, consecrata in honore beati Petri aposstolorum
                        principe, cum omnibus casis et rebus seu familiis per singulis locis et
                        vocabulis ab ea pertinentibus et aspicientibus cum integritate sua. Dono
                        insuper eidem sancto loco omnes res meas in <geogName ref="#estates/1505"
                            >finibus <placeName ref="#places/262">Laudensi</placeName></geogName>,
                        id sunt cortes meas in <geogName ref="#estates/1507"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/1905"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                                >Prata</placeName></geogName> seu in <geogName ref="#estates/1506"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/1904"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve"
                                >Montemalo</placeName></geogName> sive etiam <geogName
                            ref="#estates/1509"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                            >corte que appellatur <placeName ref="#places/1907"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                                >Mediolanense</placeName></geogName>; res etiam meas in <geogName
                            ref="#estates/1510">finibus Cremonensi</geogName>, id sunt cortes meas
                            <geogName ref="#estates/112"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/354"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                                >Sexto</placeName></geogName> et <geogName ref="#estates/1508"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/1906"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve"
                                >Tencaria</placeName></geogName>. Dono etiam et confero in ipsum
                        sanctum locum cortes meas que michi in <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Dowry"
                            >dotis</rs> nomine advenerunt de eodem domino et vir meus, id sunt
                            <geogName ref="#estates/110"
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/141"
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches"
                                >Campomiliacio</placeName></geogName> in finibus Modinensibus et
                        Corte Nova et <geogName ref="#estates/42"
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve #Slave"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/34"
                                key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve #Slave"
                                >Piguniaria</placeName></geogName> seu et alias cortes meas
                            <geogName ref="#estates/194"><placeName ref="#places/435"
                                >Feline</placeName></geogName> qui nominatur <placeName
                            ref="#places/33"
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve #Slave"
                                ><geogName ref="#estates/40"
                                key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve #Slave"
                                >Vuardestalla</geogName></placeName> et <geogName ref="#estates/38"
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve #Slave"
                            >corte mea <placeName ref="#places/32"
                                key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve"
                                >Luciaria</placeName></geogName>
                        <geogName ref="#estates/1503" key="#Curtes">finibus <placeName
                                ref="#places/191" key="#Curtes">Regensibus</placeName></geogName>,
                        cum omnibus <rs key="#Landed_possessions">casis et rebus</rs> sive <rs
                            key="#Slave">familias</rs> per singulis locis ab pertinentibus ab eis
                        quamque et de singulis hominibus in nostrum ius dominiumque adquisitas.
                        Offero insuper et confirmo cortes mea in <geogName ref="#estates/111"
                            >comitatu <placeName ref="#places/351"
                            >Stationense</placeName></geogName>, id sunt <placeName
                            ref="#places/1909"
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve"
                                ><geogName ref="#estates/1511"
                                key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve"
                                >Cabroi</geogName></placeName> et <placeName ref="#places/503"
                            key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve"
                                ><geogName ref="#estates/114"
                                key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve"
                                >Masina</geogName></placeName> ad usu et perpetuam possessionem in
                        eiusdem venerabili loci habendas; eo videlicet ordine ut in predicto loco
                        Masini ad <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/191" key="#Churches #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve">ecclesiam
                            Sancte genitricis Marie</orgName> decem monachi vel canonici excubare
                        debeant et exorare iugiter pro remedio anime sepedicti gloriosissimi
                        imperatoris domini et senioris mei et mercedem meam; et detur eis ab
                        abbatissa que pro tempore fuerit per annum convenientia subsidia in
                        alimentis et vestibus seu reliquis corporis necessitatibus. Similiter etiam
                        confirmo habendas iamdicto venerabili sanctuario cortes meas in comitatu
                        Bulgarense, id sunt Brunago et Trencate; verum etiam et cortem meam in
                        Salmatam, que est in maritimis; et <geogName ref="#estates/80" key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve">cortem meam
                            <placeName ref="#places/362" key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Fiscal_reserve">Villulam</placeName></geogName> que est
                        in comitatu Mantuano; sed et salinas meas in Comiaclo Pado, quod michi
                        legibus pertinere debent. Quas supradictas cortes in prenominatas cortes in
                        prenominatis finibus et comitatibus cum omni integritate et possessione
                        earum cunctisque adiacentiis et pertinentiis earum in rebus mobilibus et
                        immobilibus seu utriusque sexus et diverse condictionis familiis ubicumque
                        michi lege ac ratione competit vel in posterum competere legibus poterit per
                        imperatoria precepta sive per emptione et donationum cartulas </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
